name: Waco Table Toppers
description: Title unknown of this original 2015 Vibrant Cows Painting. First Vibrant Cows Painting ever to be included in an auction, which happen to be for Wacos Table Topper. The painting sold in auction for $1500 to a woman from Oklahoma. One print was made of this painting and that as well was put into the auction. The print was framed and set in resin. Its whereabouts are unknown. Original painting measured 48x36 inches, acrylic on canvas.
